You need to install several libraries before to compile the toolkit.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Please follow the instructions provided by the offical sites to 
install following library.
* OpenGL
http://www.opengl.org/
http://freeglut.sourceforge.net/

* CGAL

http://www.cgal.org/

* TCLAP

http://tclap.sourceforge.net/
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Edit *Makefile* in root directory, to make sure the configuration is 
correct, and type

make all

to build library and compile the software, this will generate a binary 
excutable one in the current directly:

MeshTK

and dynamic library and header files in directory

include
lib


